highlights.text: “Alucin” by Eugenio Esquivel, Grupo Marca Registrada, and Sebastian Esquivel is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 32 spots at #66.
“yes, and?” by Ariana Grande is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #1.
21 Savage has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “redrum” is the highest at #8.
“lovely (with Khalid)” by Billie Eilish and Khalid has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 300 weeks straight.
